---
title: Pulled Chicken Burger with cheesy chorizo chips and salad
description: Cheesy chorizo chips, chipotle pulled chicken and rich brioche buns—this is an indulgent meal with many appealing elements to choose from. The crunchy salad tomato slices add a pleasing touch of freshness to an already abundant recipe.
